<p class="ql-align-center">今天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们在一辆<strong>冠道</strong>的<strong>后备厢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">装满了<strong>礼品袋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并邀请到三位车友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起将礼品袋取出并平铺在地上...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到底会<strong>占多大面积</strong>？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=227242362&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整整一个篮球场的礼品袋</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被冠道的后备厢空间轻松容纳，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">相信这是比数字更有力的展示。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">当然，不仅是<strong>3000个</strong>礼品袋，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冠道的后备厢也能让你更自由舒适的出行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8c4f241ef7e047b09958096cc2a3df09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一句话形容</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果你身高在<strong>180cm</strong>左右</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">坐在后排完全可以</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">既<strong>“葛优躺”</strong>又翘<strong>“二郎腿”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">此外，冠道后排中央地板<strong>纯平</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">即使是坐在中间的乘客</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">腿部也能得到放松</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">后排表现已经足可观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那加上后备厢呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201208/9caca82b636d4674a947dfc31404bb6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">根据有车以后的实测数据显示</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冠道的后备厢</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在不放倒二排座椅的情况下</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">可放入<strong>13</strong>个<strong>30×30×30cm</strong>的标准纸箱</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在同级别车型中表现出色</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果您只是单纯的享受二人世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">对于后排的需求不是很大</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那么将第二排座椅放倒之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>后备厢</strong>的容积则<strong>大</strong>的<strong>超乎</strong>你的<strong>想象</strong></p>
